        <h1>&#10022; Privacy & Policy &#10022;</h1>
        <p>
          At <strong>Book My Bite</strong>, your privacy and trust are extremely
          important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
          store, and protect your information when you use our website. By
          accessing Book My Bite, you agree to the practices described below.
          Our goal is to maintain a transparent, safe, and responsible
          environment for all users.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Information We Collect</strong><br />
          We collect information that you voluntarily provide when you create an
          account, list a restaurant, write a review, or interact with our
          platform. This information may include your name, email address,
          contact details, restaurant details, images, and reviews. We may also
          collect basic technical data such as your IP address, browser type,
          device information, and pages you visit on our site. This helps us
          improve your experience and maintain platform security.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>How We Use Your Information</strong><br />
          Your information helps us deliver a smooth, personalized, and
          functional experience. We use the information to create restaurant
          listings, process user reviews, manage accounts, respond to messages,
          improve search and filter accuracy, and protect the platform from
          misuse. We may also use your data for analytics to understand what
          users search for, what features work well, and how we can improve Book
          My Bite for everyone.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Image & Restaurant Data</strong><br />
          When you upload images or restaurant details, they may be stored on
          third-party services such as Cloudinary or cloud databases. These
          files help other users discover restaurants with accurate visuals and
          information. By uploading images, you grant us permission to display
          them on our platform as part of your listing or review.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Cookies & Tracking</strong><br />
          Book My Bite may use cookies or small data files to remember your
          preferences, improve loading speed, and provide better browsing
          suggestions. You can manage or disable cookies through your browser
          settings, but some features may not work correctly without them.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>How We Protect Your Data</strong><br />
          We use secure servers, encrypted connections, and authentication
          checks to keep your data safe. While no online platform can guarantee
          100% protection, we actively monitor and update our security practices
          to keep your information protected from unauthorized access or misuse.
          We do not sell or share your personal details with advertisers or
          unknown third parties.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Third-Party Services</strong><br />
          Book My Bite may integrate third-party tools like Cloudinary,
          analytics services, or map providers. These services follow their own
          privacy policies and may collect basic technical information. We
          ensure that we only work with trusted, reputable platforms to maintain
          user safety.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>User Rights</strong><br />
          You have full rights to view, update, or delete your personal data. If
          you want to remove your account, edit a restaurant listing, or request
          deletion of any content you uploaded, you can contact us anytime. We
          respect your control over your information.
        </p>

